name: FLYING THE DORNIER 328! Central Mountain Air Calgary to Edmonton
description:
Central Mountain Air, or CMA, is a Canadian regional airline that flies mostly within Alberta and British Columbia. They fly a fleet of Dash 8s, Beech 1900s, and Dornier 328s - the subject of today's trip report!

See what I thought of Central Mountain Air and their unique Dornier in this flight review from Calgary to Edmonton.
